along.' So these are all run-on sentences

00:36:38.020 --> 00:36:45.230
even though they're really quite short. What
they need is, what they need is a something

00:36:45.230 --> 00:36:50.530
to separate the two main clauses. So the one
I can reach [laughs] [audience laughter] 'Beth

00:36:50.530 --> 00:36:56.760
went to a yoga class Ben came along' you could
put a period there. You could make it two

00:36:56.760 --> 00:37:01.840
